Team














Distribution and Consultant Relations.


The distribution and consultant relations team is committed to creating a loyal and satisfied customer base, building vital relationships with our consultants and communicating the products, personnel and strategies of LGIMA. Our customer-led focus is the cornerstone of all our marketing activities and the team stays very close to the changing needs of our customers. We also work with investment consultants to ensure the most effective investment solutions are provided to clients.   



